title: John Coltrane - A Love Supreme 1965 / Verve 2008
description:
John Coltrane / A Love Supreme / 1965

Verve Reissue / 2008



It is still one of the most essential landmark jazz albums, everything on A Love Supreme is a work of beauty, salvation, and a welcome to everyone who opens the door to a world of a discovery that you never see.


CD / 2008 / 320Kbps


Tracklist:
01. A Love Supreme, Part I: Acknowledgement
02. A Love Supreme, Part II: Resolution
03. A Love Supreme, Part III: Pursuance
04. A Love Supreme, Part IV: Psalm

McCoy Tyner - piano
Jimmy Garrison - bass
